high_descs: Turn around and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and step forward to face the kitchen table.
Cut the lettuce on the table into slices.
Turn around and step forward to face the fridge.
Place the knife in the fridge.
Turn around and walk forward to face the kitchen table.
Pick up a lettuce slice on the kitchen table.
Turn around and step forward to face the fridge.
Cool the lettuce slice in the fridge and remove it.
Turn left and walk forward to face the sink.
Place the lettuce slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To cool a lettuce slice plus place it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and go to the table.
Cut the lettuce on the table.
Turn around and go to the fridge.
Put the knife on the second shelf in the fridge.
Turn around and go back to the table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce.
Turn around and go back to the fridge.
Chill the slice of lettuce in the fridge and pick it back up.
Turn left and head to the sink.
Put the slice of lettuce in front of the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of lettuce in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left for one step, turn left and walk straight to the counter and stop.
Pick up the large knife with a yellow handle.
Turn around and take four steps, turn right walk to the table.
Slice up the lettuce with the knife
Turn left for two steps, turn left again and go to the refrigerator
Open the refrigerator, put the knife on the on the second shelf of the fridge, on the left side of the shelf with the knife pointed to the right, then shut the doors.
Turn left for three steps, turn left and go to the table.
Pick up a slice of lettuce, the first thin slice from the left.
Turn left for three steps, turn left and go to the refrigerator.
Open the refrigerator put the lettuce slice on the top shelf directly above the knife and shut the door, wait a few seconds, open the fridge, take out the lettuce and shut the door.
Turn left for five steps, turn left for six steps and turn right to face the sink.
Place the lettuce slice on its edge in front of the potato in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled slice of lettuce in the sink.
